{"tid":1838331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據報英國將容許華為參與當地5G網絡開發","createTime":"2020-01-24T03:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T14:07:00.000Z","uid":37554,"like":4,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ce95d16d0f1c5d5be1a322dc7c03b94e9a54809f","tid":1838331,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】英國據報不會理會美國的施壓，許容中國電訊設備商華為參與當地5G網絡開發。<br />\n<br />\n彭博引述消息人士稱，若果排除華為在英國5G網絡開發，電訊公司將面臨高達數以十億英鎊計的成本，同時令英國首相約翰遜推出全光纖寬頻計劃的時間表推遲4年，指英國當局將於下周在國會宣布，容許華為參與英國5G網絡開發中不太敏感的部分。<br />\n<br />\n路透則報道，當局將提出禁止華為參與5G網絡開發中，敏感和涉及數據密集的核心部分，以及參與政府機密系統。"},{"pid":"7904c9683ec02d730d0cd15cac6ab4e80ed2097c","tid":1838331,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:41:46.000Z","msg":"綏靖政策2.0"},{"pid":"13febec35b247d6b8b534967f6fb478735b05f80","tid":1838331,"uid":88133,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"肺炎5G網絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61251dffdefd0ec887d80031c9cc23817c1a2bc2","tid":1838331,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"要日防夜防，何必呢？"},{"pid":"22a7b8f8d50df5fd9e300400c98a6688a0cb54ae","tid":1838331,"uid":10757,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:43:31.000Z","msg":"5眼聯盟 out"},{"pid":"db2a76f447b0b02d5e7ede7f76b3915d4a2d46f8","tid":1838331,"uid":167548,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:44:13.000Z","msg":"利申想見證日落帝國解體"},{"pid":"bdfaadff380ce3b8baaa06de45f666a07a3eeb45","tid":1838331,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:45:22.000Z","msg":"幾時公佈埋容許武漢肺炎入英國"},{"pid":"89f2278ca2419df5bc071bc3d5c9c46e8659411f","tid":1838331,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:46:08.000Z","msg":"俾你英國貪平起左<br />\n之後美帝封殺全部變垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><